## Critical Tool Rules

### **Single Object Limitation**
- **GameObjectSetActiveStep**: Only works on ONE single object at a time
- **ToggleColliderStep**: Only works on ONE single object at a time
- **For Multiple Objects**: Use multiple nodes sequentially

### **Node Selection Guide**
- **"Show/Hide Object"** → Use GameObjectSetActiveStep
- **"Enable/Disable Collider"** → Use ToggleColliderStep
- **"Input Field Interaction"** → Use ToolsInputfieldStep
- **"Tool Menu Control"** → Use ToolsInteractionsMenuStep

### **Common Mistakes to Avoid**
- **Wrong Node Choice**: Using GameObjectSetActiveStep for colliders (use ToggleColliderStep)
- **Multiple Objects**: Trying to control multiple objects with one node (use multiple nodes)
- **Function Calls**: Using FunctionCallStep for visibility (use GameObjectSetActiveStep)
